    <div class="case__description">
      <h2>How good are you at assessing risk?</h2>

      <p class="highlight">The insurance company Dina Försäkringar wanted to help people answer that question. Edelman Deportivo created a concept and design that we implemented.</p>

      <div class="additional">
        <p>Resultatet blev spelet Dina Risker. Spelaren får här under tidspress jämföra olika risker, som slumpas fram, mot varandra för att sedan få ett omdöme om ens riskbedömningsförmåga.</p>

        <p>It all ended up in the game Dina Risker. Within time limitations the player have to compare eight different risks against each other ending up getting a judgement on how good he or she is assesing risks.</p>

        <p>When the game is over the player also gets an unique link with the result to share and brag about on the web. As well as a more in depth information regarding the different risks that were assesed.</p>

